Infection with ranavirus, Chinese Taipei
----------------------------------------
Information received on [and dated] 10 Apr 2014 from Dr Ping-Cheng Yang, director, Animal Technology Institute Taiwan, Council of Agriculture, Taiwan, Chinese Taipei

Summary
Report type: immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 12 Jan 2014
Date of pre-confirmation of the event: 8 Apr 2014
Reason for notification: 1st occurrence of a listed disease
Manifestation of disease: clinical disease
Causal agent: _Ranavirus_
Nature of diagnosis: laboratory (advanced),
This event pertains to the whole country

New outbreaks (3)
Outbreak 1: Jiuru Township, Pingtung County
Date of start of the outbreak: 12 Jan 2014
Outbreak status: continuing (or date resolved not provided)
Epidemiological unit: farm
Water type: fresh water
Population type: farmed
Population system: closed
Affected animals:
Species / Morbidity [per cent] / Mortality [per cent] / Susceptible / Cases / Deaths / Destroyed / Slaughtered
